asgn2Tests

Class CustomerTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • asgn2Tests.CustomerTests

  • public class CustomerTests
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that tests the that tests the asgn2Customers.PickUpCustomer, asgn2Customers.DriverDeliveryCustomer, asgn2Customers.DroneDeliveryCustomer classes. Note that an instance of asgn2Customers.DriverDeliveryCustomer should be used to test the functionality of the asgn2Customers.Customer abstract class.
